The **new tax regime** (default from FY 2024-25) offers lower slab rates but removes most deductions. The **old tax regime** allows deductions like 80C, 80D, HRA, and home loan interest. This calculator computes your tax under both regimes side by side so you can choose the one that saves you more money for FY 2026-27.
